      "description": "This E92 M3 is a mechanically sound example featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering 414 hp with a soaring 8,400 RPM redline. The drivetrain is paired with a 7-speed M Double-Clutch Transmission (DCT) providing crisp, rev-matched downshifts and lightning-fast gear transitions. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by an M Variable Differential Lock and a multi-link rear suspension setup that maintains excellent kinematic integrity. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive throttle actuator service and a fresh transaxle fluid flush. Equipped with cross-drilled ventilated rotors and M-specific damping, this vehicle offers precise turn-in and high-speed stability for the discerning enthusiast.",
